title: Having Confidence In Yourself | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Having Confidence In Yourself | Joel Osteen
description:
Don't let negative thoughts limit your potential. Reprogram your mind to dwell on the good things God says about you. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
